Board of Directors of the Company in their meeting held on May 30, 2024 approve and taken on record the following items: 
1. Consideration and approval of audited financial result for the year ended March 31, 2024;
2. Independent Audit report in pursuance with Regulations 33 of SEBI (LODR) Regulations, 2015 for the financial year March 31, 2024.
